Package sudoku.model

Class SudokuBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • sudoku.model.SudokuBoard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Board>, Board
    public class SudokuBoard
extends java.lang.Object
implements Board
    Board model for sudoku game with nxm inner boxes, n=length of inner box-row and m=length of inner box-col.

        minor - The minor coordinate component of the cell.

        public int compareTo​(Board other)
